Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:45.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ame agari no sora wo aogu tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:45.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to \Nthe sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:07.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:07.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has \Nfaded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:12.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:12.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After losing his brother Ace during \Nthe War of the Best against the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was consumed with unbearable sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is, however, an untold \Nstory of the brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...10 years ago in the East \NBlue - Luffy and Ace as boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo who became brother to Luffy and Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.51,0:04:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has been brought home by \Nhis father, a member of the nobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do as you say. I'll \Nlive as you want so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...please don't hurt these two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you. They're very important \Nto me, they're my brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all have to keep quiet about the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if someone outside the \Ntown finds out about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're special! If you're \Nfrom a noble family...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Fire Has Been Set! The \NGray Terminal in Crisis!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I know. What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're setting boxes of oil and \Nexplosives all over the Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have to tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you! Watch out! You have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We got him!\N--Hey, relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Burn down the Gray Terminal?! \NWhy are you doing that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! Don't scream! We can't \Nlet anyone else know about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is serious! I gotta tell everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a bad guy just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to not to scream. \NHey, hold them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the mastermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was oil and explosives in the boxes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you guys carried yesterday and today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's gonna be a massive \Nfire that no one can escape from.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No...\N--Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even punk kids like you two are freaking out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now you know about the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask you something before the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, you two, do you have a \Ntreasure hidden away somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've given me nothing but \Ntrouble! You're such a bad son!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was right to adopt another \Nchild just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up, dad! I gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people that I have \Nto help! Dad! Dad! Open Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:49.40,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,EDGE TOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong with the Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it burning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best game I've ever played!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-Boss! Boss! You gotta see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you screaming about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The sky in the north, look!\N--Is it the town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, closer than that! Must be \Nthe Gray Terminal! It's on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:29.15,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,DOWNTOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:29.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? It's like a wildfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's never happened before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous - evacuate Edge Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:39.62,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,EDGE TOWN--GREAT GATE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All residents must head to Downtown!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the lifesaving and fire \Nextinguishing to us military!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We made it to the Great Gate!\N--We're safe now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only protect the residents here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:09:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No way!\N--How can you do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let us get in!\N--Help us, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Everybody, wake up!\N--You gotta run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The fire is spreading all around!\N--We can't stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, give it up! \NYou gotta flee your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! The fire has gotten to the shore already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entrance to the forest is ablaze, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Where should we go?! We're stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn everything, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we complete this task,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my long-cherished dream will come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't give a damn \Nabout the other people living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if this place is so crappy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's good enough for us to hide in, King.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aware of that, Bluejam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when this is over, you \Nno longer need to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will make you and your friends \Nnobles by my authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The king will give us titles
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll live in the High \NTown as privileged nobles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We better get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get to the Great Gate! \NThe military is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, we left the brats in the hideout...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:11:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget 'em. They could've joined my crew \Nif they told me where the treasure was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools can't live long anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's closed, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic. They just don't \Nwant other people to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plan is for me to give them a sign, \Nthen they'll open the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Bluejam. Open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys, what are \Nyou doing?! Open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plan was you let us \Nevacuate from here, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not what we agreed to! You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your promise, King?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that you'd make us nobles...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You set us up? King!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bluejam, a pirate in the Gray \NTerminal, started the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought! \NNo one else would do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it to try to keep the observers \Nfrom the World Government away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How terrible he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot! It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! We didn't wanna be involved in this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get away! I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave you behind if \Nyou don't stop complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, it's hot! No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fire is everywhere outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The air is hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be alright! I'm here with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:13:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call the police! Sabo did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! You have to evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away! Stay away from the lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Be a good kid and evacuate!\N--Don't give us any trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ace... Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The royalty and nobles \Nare... behind the fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This town smells worse than Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells like rotten people!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stay here... I'll never be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...ashamed of being born a noble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They finally made a kid \Nsay this! Goa Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel. I was \Nborn in this country, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still don't have enough \Npower to change the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, you really are \Nlistening to me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and I'll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, there's no chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way to put out the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta give up the ship! \NWe can't flee to the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn the King! How could he do this to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show that bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so annoying that the sky \Nin the south is bright even in the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are sorry, your Majesty. \NLet us close the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:17:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, daddy, why are the people \Nin the Gray Terminal not humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do they have to get burned?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the phrase goes, "As a \Nman sows, so shall he reap."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They could have avoided their \Nfate just by being born nobles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Born nobles?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! They should have \Nchosen to be born nobles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, enough about those people, \Nyou have to study for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There's no way on this side!\N--We keep losing ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if those old men escaped safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be concerned \Nabout other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I don't even know where I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said that you could get away, you brats?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bluejam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you still here \Nafter setting the fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were supposed to have escaped by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're hopeless, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have an unforeseen dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are strange creatures, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you hit rock bottom, \Nyou can't stop laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.39,0:18:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We worked together - we're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to die together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't wanna die with you! \NNot in a million years!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you haven't told \Nme where you keep your treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save it for you before the fire \Ngets it. So tell me where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life is in danger and all \Nyou care about is treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't care, then tell me where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gone mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not gonna go \Nget it, it'd be a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing is done, it's gonna be \Nreduced to charcoal like my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous! That treasure is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! You and Sabo spent a lot of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo would understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What matters the most now is your...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What matters the most now is our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We keep our treasure from \Nlast 6 years in this tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright. This is not the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! I told you where it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. This is not the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.42,0:20:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means you could be lying. \NYou gotta come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Then it's gonna \Nbe too late to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you guys go on your own?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't wanna mess with me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm determined to make a come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it means stealing from kids
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can take my revenge on nobles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your brother is one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They think they're so special
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and look down on others as if we're trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo doesn't think like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the same as them, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.36,0:21:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was with you both just to feel superior!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His parents are loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't \Nhave to worry about anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.05,0:21:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a pastime for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was looking down on you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and laughing to himself holding his nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking bad about Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Sabo just wants to be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:21:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.59,0:22:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! You okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.56,0:22:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:22:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:22:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You creepy brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna make a fool out of me, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.34,0:23:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you scumbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.65,0:23:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.80,0:23:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.73,0:23:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.53,0:23:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace and Luffy are cornered by Bluejam!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.68,0:23:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trapped among the flames with no escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.43,0:23:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace stands his ground and \Nprepares to fight alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, left behind in High Town,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.84,0:23:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo finally takes action \Nto go after his dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Where can freedom be found? \NA Sad Departure of a Boy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
